# CODEOWNERS — who must review which paths.
# Replace the @your-org/* placeholders with real GitHub teams (or @users) before relying on this.
# GitHub: enable branch-protection "Require review from Code Owners" or this file gates nothing.
# Azure DevOps: this file is ignored — encode the same ownership as branch-policy required reviewers.

# Default owner for everything not matched below.
*                         @your-org/maintainers

# Risk paths — the owning team must review every change (mirror these in branch-protection).
/auth/                    @your-org/security
**/security/              @your-org/security
/iac/                     @your-org/platform
/migrations/              @your-org/data
**/alembic/               @your-org/data

# Couche-0 gate config — edits here change the delivery gate itself.
/.github/workflows/       @your-org/platform
/.pre-commit-config.yaml  @your-org/platform
/branch-protection.tf     @your-org/platform
/org-profile.yaml         @your-org/maintainers
/CODEOWNERS               @your-org/maintainers
